text: Pennington is a borough in Mercer County, in the U.S. state of New Jersey. As of the 2020 United States census, the borough's population was 2,802.Table 7. Population for the Counties and Municipalities in New Jersey: 1990, 2000 and 2010, New Jersey Department of Labor and Workforce Development, February 2011.
